Package data.petrinets

Class Summary
Arc Represents one arc in a Petri net (the connection between a place and a transition).
PetriNetCreator Generates a Petri net which integrates data from an arbitrary number of networks, complex sets and purification data sets.
Place Represents one place in a Petri net.
ToPNetGenerator Converts a Petri net to a ToPNet .places and .interactions file pair.
Transition Represents one transition in a Petri net.
XGMMLGenerator Converts a Petri net file to a Cytoscape-compatible XGMML file.
